programme.title: World Watch: Africa’s Hunter Ep9
programme.desc: Ikuti kehidupan pemangsa hebat di Zambia seperti singa, harimau bintang dan hyena, yang bersaing dalam dunia liar yang semakin mencabar. Pelbagai perubahan berlaku dari kelahiran impala serentak hingga kemunculan makhluk ganjil seperti anai-anai terbang. Alam liar Lembah ini bersedia menghadapi musim baharu. Episod kali ini mengenai ketua singa kembar dan Notch mengekalkan ikatan yang kuat antara satu sama lain dengan kebanggaan Nsefu yang terkenal yang mereka pimpin.

programme.title: Bidadari: Kerana Hafsanya Setia Ep23
programme.desc: Segalanya seakan sempurna apabila Delaila dan Ali Syukri disatukan atas dasar cinta. Tapi benarlah kata orang, kahwin pada usia muda itu banyak cabarannya. Bahtera rumah tangga mereka diuji dengan kehadiran orang ketiga dan Delaila membawa diri ke New York. Dua belas tahun kemudian, pertemuan di New York telah membuka semula kisah mereka. Wairah telah memberi amaran pada Delilah supaya jangan melawat Haifa lagi. Ali pulang ke kampung untuk melamar Delilah. Delilah mahu Ali memberi dia masa untuk memikirkannya. Wairah menyesal dengan penceraiannya bersama Ali kerana memikirkan keadaan Haifa yang rindukan Ali. Dia ingin rujuk semula dengan Ali. Pelakon: Azrel Ismail, Mona Ellen, Octovia Menrose dan Daler Yusuf.

programme.title: Cuit-Cuit: Aksara Kasih Ayah Ep13
programme.desc: Mengisahkan hubungan kasih sayang seorang ayah dengan anak angkatnya. Namun apabila dugaan mendatang bagaimana pula kisah kasihnya itu, setelah isteri yang dia sayangi pula meninggal dunia. Hari peperiksaan Hilmi telah tiba dan Badrul menyediakan sarapan pagi untuk Hilmi, Hilmi menghulurkan tangan untuk bersalam dengan ayahnya sebelum pergi mengambil peperiksaan SPM dan terharu apabila buat pertama kali, ayahnya menyambut salam Hilmi Pelakon: Saufi Qahhar, Wafiy Ilhan, Zamarul Hisham, Izreen Azminda dan Awang Hamyzan.

programme.title: Citra: Luka Di Hati Diya Ep6
programme.desc: Kisah Diya Mirza, wanita penuh trauma yang hidup dalam ketakutan dan sering dibuli. Kehadiran Remmy, staf baharu yang naif namun jujur, membuka pintu hati Diya yang sekian lama tertutup. Namun, kisah silam kembali menghantui bila ayah tiri Diya muncul semula. Dalam pelarian dan pengorbanan, cinta mereka diuji. Mampukah mereka bertahan atau hati akan terus dilukai?. Sara menolak permintaan datin untuk mengahwini Dato kerana Sara sudah mempunyai pilihan hati iaitu Shukri. Remy dan Megat meraikan diya kerana berhenti kerja dan berpindah ke johor. Ibu Diya Rohani di tempat kerja. Pelakon: Isyariana, Niezam Zaidi, Fauzi Nawawi, Lisdawati, Sherry Ibrahim, Fikhree Bakar, Kodi Rasheed, Lia Natalia, Azlan Komeng, Kak Girl, Syed Mirfan, Nonny Nadirah, dan Sanjna Suri.

programme.title: Spektra: Derhaka Cinta Jebat Ep15
programme.desc: Semua berpunca kerana rasa dendam, salah faham dan ditambah pula dengan ego yang tinggi melangit, sanggup Jebat Zulkarnain menzalimi Aisyah Humaira isterinya sendiri. Bijaknya Jebat mengatur rancangan agar Aisyah jatuh cinta padanya hingga membawa kepada sebuah perkahwinan dengan niat ingin membalas dendam. Aisyah Humaira, suatu ketika dahulu pernah menjalinkan hubungan cinta dengan adik lelaki Jebat, iaitu Tuah Iskandar. Tanpa usul periksa Jebat menjatuhkan hukuman tanpa memberi peluang kepada Aisyah untuk menjelaskan segala-galanya. Aisyah dituduh berlaku curang dengan Tuah dan menjadi penyebab musibah yang menimpa adik lelaki kesayangannya. Aisyah benar-benar kecewa. Jebat mendustai cintanya. Dia dinikahi Jebat bukan untuk disayang, dicintai sepenuh hati tapi Jebat punya agendanya sendiri. Misi Jebat hanyalah satu, melunaskan dendamnya dan membalas balik segala kesengsaraan Tuah yang kononnya dikhianati Aisyah dahulu. Pelakon: Elvina Mohamad, Azlee Khairi, Ikmal Amry, Mimi Ernida, Nina Fazurina, Wilma Muhammad dan Aznah Hamid.

programme.title: Impak Aksi Ep9
programme.desc: Program berkongsi memaparkan aktiviti-aktiviti lasak seperti motorcross, zorb ball, water absailing, paramotor, rock climbing, water rafting, 4x4, tomoi, mountain bike, paintball, kayak, martial art dan mix martial arts. Menariknya dalam setiap episod menampilkan kemuculan artis jemputan mencuba aktiviti lasak yang dikongsikan. Antara artis termasuklah Alam Wakaka, Aepul Drama Band, Syed Ali, Azrel Ismail, Nazrief Nazri, dan Farish Aziz. Saksikan cabaran sukan lasak Paintball bersama Saharul Ridzwan dan Syed Ali.

programme.title: Ekspresi Eko Ep11
programme.desc: Program majalah bertemakan perlancongan yang memberikan fokus kepada ecotourism atau perlancongan eko yang terdapat dalam 12 negeri di seluruh Malaysia. Menampilkan hos Mas Khan, konsep keseluruhan iaitu melancong, menikmati keindahan sambil melakukan aktiviti-aktiviti yang disediakan di lokasi berkenaan. Fokus rancangan adalah kepada memperkenalkan lokasi pelancongan eko atau ecotourism, mempromosi aktiviti berkaitan dan tip-tip berguna termasuk`do & dont apabila berada di lokasi berkenaan. Saksikan perjalanan Nurata Amin ke Taman Negara Bako, Kuching.

programme.title: Lubuk S4 Ep01

programme.title: Pintu Neraka
programme.desc: Kisah ini mengisahkan tentang Kamasani, seorang tokoh perniagaan yang menghidap kanser tahap akhir, yang mencari Mahabub, seorang pertapa misteri yang dikhabarkan memiliki penawar. Selepas menjalani rawatan yang mahal, Kamasani merasakan penyakitnya semakin berkurang, namun dia mula mengalami kesan sampingan yang serius; dia berhalusinasi dan menjadi ganas. Titik perubahan berlaku apabila Vida, seorang wartawan televisyen, membongkar konspirasi ghaib Mahabub yang melibatkan nama-nama besar. Kamasani akhirnya sedar bahawa ramai yang telah menderita atau mati akibat keengganannya menerima takdir sendiri, lalu bertekad untuk membetulkan segalanya.

programme.title: Black S2 EP4 Ep4
programme.desc: Black menolong Sofia menyelamatkan seseorang yang rapat dengan Sofia tapi itu hanya menyebabkan mereka hampir maut. Semuanya tampak ada kaitan dengan runtuhan Pusat Membeli-Belah Seri Setia. Sementara itu, Aisya menerima tekanan daripada pembunuh upahan Si Jari Tengah untuk mencari pita video yang sukar ditemui - kegagalan yang akan membahayakan nyawa Malik. Siasatan Borhan mengejutkan dirinya apabila dia mendapati mangsa dalam kesnya adalah seseorang yang dia pernah kenal. Lokman kecewa apabila dia nampak abangnya sangat tamak mahu mengambil-alih Insurans Mahkota.

programme.title: Black S2 EP5 Ep5
programme.desc: Percubaan Black untuk menangkap 419 gagal akibat teleportasinya yang tidak berfungsi. Sementara itu, menggunakan fail kes ayahnya, Sofia menjejak pembunuh yang disyaki, hingga terjebak dalam situasi yang membahayakan nyawa. Aisya mendapati Black merahsiakan kebenaran penting daripada Sofia yang mengugat hubungan mereka. Borhan menyusul petunjuk yang membawanya kembali ke Seri Setia.

Kapten polis Gilbert terganggu oleh seorang wartawan Cina yang menulis cerita tentang skuadnya, isteri detektif Emilien baru sahaja mengumumkan bahawa dia hamil, dan pemandu teksi Daniel sedang mengalami krisis hubungan. Selepas rentetan kesilapan di mana pencuri mengakali polis berkali-kali dengan wartawan di sana untuk merakam semuanya, Daniel dan teksi supernya masuk.

Semasa menjalani syif malam, lelaki itu dan rakan sekerjanya yang bekerja lebih masa mengalami pertemuan menyeramkan yang membuatkan mereka merenung tingkah laku dan kepercayaan mereka.

programme.desc: Joey, pemilik rancangan televisyen "Merungkai Misteri", telah dipanggil ke Kampung Bonang untuk menyiasat misteri kematian ngeri Cikgu Hassan. Berikutan kematiannya, penduduk kampung mendakwa rohnya kelihatan berkeliaran di kampung mencari pengganti baru. Pada masa yang sama, anak perempuannya Julia sering tidak sihat sekarang kerana diganggu oleh makhluk ghaib. Untuk membersihkan nama Cikgu Hassan, Joey menculik Lufty, seorang lelaki yang tanpa disedari terlibat dalam perkara ini semasa mencari pekerjaan, untuk menjadi krunya semasa siasatan. Misteri semakin mendalam apabila Joey dan Lufty, disertai Julia, diganggu oleh semangat Penunggu Busut ketika dalam perjalanan ke Busut dan mereka tersesat.

Dia menjalankan siasatan dan menghantar orang bawahannya, Osman, untuk menyamar untuk membongkar kebenaran di rumah penginapan itu. Bagaimanapun, Osman hilang, dan Fadil mengikutnya ke rumah penginapan. Dalam perjalanan, dia melihat figura gelap di hadapan dan merempuhnya, menyedari bahawa sesuatu yang penting sedang berlaku.

programme.desc: Yavuz, yang telah berpisah dengan isterinya Aye, ialah seorang guru kelas yang menjalani kehidupan biasa antara sekolah dan rumah. Kehidupan Yavuz berubah sama sekali apabila seorang pelajar perempuan bernama Amber masuk ke dalam kelasnya, seorang gadis yang tidak pernah berbicara dengan sesiapa. Sehari sebelum Amber hadir ke sekolah, Yavuz sebenarnya telah melihatnya di dalam mimpinya.

programme.title: Ragam Pemandu
programme.desc: Pemandu yang setia dan tidak pernah mengeluh, Hamid tidak disukai oleh isteri tuannya, Rubiah. Tuannya, Rahim pula seorang yang baik hati dan sukakan Hamid. Dia sering membantu membiayai pelajaran anak-anak Hamid dan menyelesaikan masalah yang dihadapi olehnya. Satu pertengkaran menyebabkan Hamid berhenti kerja namun Rahim tampil membantu mengambilnya bekerja di syarikat insurans miliknya.

programme.title: Anita Dunia Ajaib
programme.desc: Rumahtangga Amir dan Asmah berubah setelah mereka didatangi seorang pembantu rumah misteri yang membantu mendapatkan mereka cahaya mata. Selepas melahirkan anak dalam tempoh yang singkat, satu demi satu insiden aneh menimpa ahli keluarga dan kenalan mereka.

programme.title: Pemburu Bayang
programme.desc: Zamri merupakan seorang bekas banduan yang ingin memulakan hidup baru bersama keluarganya. Namun, nasib tidak menyebelahinya apabila dia diburu kumpulan yang diketuai Ramon. Adik Zamri, Awie ialah seorang penyanyi kumpulan rock popular yang sedang menjalinkan hubungan cinta bersama Ella, yang juga penyanyi rock. Sesuatu terjadi yang menyebabkan Awie dan Ella putus hubungan. Manakala, Zamri pula diuji dengan pelbagai dugaan apabila isterinya dibunuh dengan kejam.

programme.title: Matinya Seorang Patriot
programme.desc: Pengerusi Melati Holdings, Haji Saaban meninggal dunia secara tiba-tiba yang menimbulkan keraguan tentang kematiannya. Safuan mengesyaki bahawa kematian bapanya ada kena mengena dengan syarikat bapanya. Saiful yang pada mulanya ingin membalas dendam kematian bapanya mula berubah apabila jatuh cinta dengan anak kepada ahli lembaga pengarah. Safuan menganggap Saiful telah mengkhianati keluarga mereka.

programme.title: Dia Ibuku
programme.desc: Rohani perlu bekerja keras untuk menyara anak-anaknya, Jamal dan Jamil kerana statusnya sebagai seorang janda. Perjumpaan itu membawa kembali kenangan silam yang pahit.

programme.title: Leftenan Adnan
programme.desc: Adnan memutuskan untuk menjadi seorang tentera dalam pasukan Askar Melayu setelah dikunjungi anggota tentera British yang datang ke kampungnya untuk merekrut lebih ramai anak tempatan. Tidak direstui keluarga, Adnan nekad untuk mengikuti latihan ketenteraan di Port Dickson. Perjuangan Leftenan Adnan dalam mempertahankan Tanah Melayu memberikan inspirasi kepada ramai anak muda tempatan.

programme.title: Bintang Malam
programme.desc: Selepas dua belas tahun berlayar, Yazid dan Johari akhirnya pulang semula ke tanah air. Yazid pula keluar mencari Aisah di bandar - tetapi berdepan dengan pelbagai konflik dan tragedi.

programme.title: Penyamun Tarbus
programme.desc: Tuan Said seorang yang kaya raya tetapi sering mengelat dari membayar cukai, menyimpan semua rekod di dalam peti besi miliknya. Tidak ingin rahsianya diketahui, diupahnya penyiasat penyendirian untuk menjejaki penyamun itu.

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa Ep291
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa Ep291
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: The Sound of Happiness Ep127
programme.desc: Wu is a senior police officer has always wanted a son to carry his family name and join the force. However, he and wife are bequeathed with four daughters! As a doting father, his chief objective is to help them find happiness in their marriages. In this charming drama, Wu & his wife become their daughters greatest haven, through the ups and downs they face as married women.

programme.title: 2025 Tainan Summer Music Festival 2025 Ep1
programme.desc: The 2025 Tainan Summer Music Festival is a two-day concert event featuring a dynamic lineup of top Taiwanese pop and rock artists, including Bii, TRASH, JUD, Men Envy Children, and more. With themed nights such as Idol Night and Band Night, the festival offers high-energy live performances and spectacular fireworks, celebrating the vibrant spirit of Taiwans summer music scene. 2025TRASHJUD,

programme.title: Have A Nice Dream Ep95
programme.desc: Five young professionals with different life skills, team up for two days and one night trip, leading the audiance to explore the good life of nature and the beauty of the land of Taiwan. 5

programme.title: Just for You Ep18
programme.desc: Two brothers, living just 300 meters apart, lead vastly different lives. The elder, Kai-Teng Chiao, a former athlete turned plumber, gave up his dreams to support his family and finds unexpected healing through a connection with a distant, cold-hearted prosecutor. Meanwhile, the younger, Hsi-Ming Chiao, a successful lawyer, is forced to confront the painful past he buried, which includes his breakup and his fathers suicide, when he meets Pao-Chi Hsu, the woman who holds the key to the memories he lost a decade ago.

programme.title: Better Days
programme.desc: In this Oscar nominee for Best International Feature Film, Nian faces relentless bullying from her peers as she prepares for her college entrance exam. Fate leads her to streetwise punk Bei, but before they can retreat into their own world, both are embroiled in a murder investigation that will change their lives forever.

programme.title: Death Notice
programme.desc: A serial killer leaves death notices in a city, stating when, how and who he will murder. Even if the victims report it to the police and receive protection, the killer can still break through and execute them. While the police sets up a special task force in response, they expose an even bigger conspiracy behind.

programme.title: Kung Fu Mahjong 2
programme.desc: Fanny appears to be an ordinary housewife but is in fact a mahjong expert. Deeply in love with her husband, she loses to a seductive woman, Curvy, both on the mahjong table and in competing for her husbands love. With the help from her mahjong master, Fanny vows to take on Curvy in the Mahjong King tournament!

programme.title: Far Far Away
programme.desc: A 28-year-old IT geek has only been in love once. Surprisingly, he ends up getting romantically involved with five different women this year and the one thing they have in common is that they all live in far flung areas of Hong Kong. After taking five intensive relationship courses within these 365 days, will he find the-one?

programme.title: Ah Boys to Men 2
programme.desc: Continuing from Ah Boys to Men, Ken returns to barracks, determined to change because of his bedridden father, and becomes a model recruit. However, his comrades think Ken wants to flatter and show off only, and repel him. Although Ken wants to explain, misunderstanding gets deepen through days. Can they unite and overcome the challenge together?

programme.title: The Brotherhood of Rebel
programme.desc: Chai, a triad member, helps his childhood friend Meow flee Hong Kong after discovering that Meow attempted to kill his triad boss. 17 years later, Chai becomes a key member of the triad. When he runs into Meow one day, he knows that his gang will kill Meow if they find him. Caught between triad and brotherhood, what will Chai choose?

programme.title: The Exodus
programme.desc: A low-ranking cop discovers a group of women, including his superior, Madam Fang and his wife, plotting to eliminate the world of men.

programme.title: Grandmaster, The
programme.desc: Directed by the acclaimed filmmaker Wong Kar Wai, this epic action feature begins in Foshan when Ip Man, the martial arts master from the south, takes up a challenge by ageing northern master Gong Yu Tian. Ip Man wins the fight, but is then defeated by Gong Yu Tians daughter Gong Er, with whom he forms an emotional bond

programme.title: Back Home
programme.desc: Wing has been able to see ghosts since young. When his mothers suicide attempt forces him to return to Hong Kong and the home he ran away from, he discovers that the horrific visions that once haunted him have become worse. Caught between the living and the dead, Wing must bring the truth to light to be free.

programme.title: Maoshan Heavenly Master
programme.desc: Prisoner Chi flees away under Master Zhangs custody, causing the latter to be expelled from his clan. On his way to find Chi, Master Zhang arrives at a place where many people vanish for no reason. He soon discovers that it is Chi who captures them in his training to become a serpent demon. The war between human and demon has just begun!

programme.title: Bullet and Brain
programme.desc: Nine years ago, two legendary criminals, Bullet and Brain, vowed not to kill and lie before they disappeared. Both now return for a mission - to protect the granddaughter of the triad boss. Can they succeed without breaking their vows?

programme.title: Quan Dao: The Journey of a Boxer
programme.desc: Ah Niu learns boxing from Uncle Xing, the boss of a boxing studio, since young and uses his skills to help the weak fight villains. When Xings son attempts drug trafficking to save his fathers studio but fails and is brutally beaten up, Ah Niu accepts a death combat challenge so as to help him take revenge.

programme.title: Band Four
programme.desc: An aspiring singer of an indie band called Band Four reunites with her estranged guitarist father following the death of her mother. Together with her half-sister and her nine-year-old son, the newly reunited family come together to support each other through their love and passion for music.

programme.title: Cloudy Mountain
programme.desc: When a decade-long tunnel project is about to complete, an earthquake strikes and leads to a series of subsidence and landslides. The tunnel and a nearby town are at stake. A retired soldier and his son step up to try and stop the disasters at source. Will the authority decide to blow up the tunnel to save the 160,000 people in town?

programme.title: Inner Senses
programme.desc: Haunted by recurring visions stemming from past traumas, Yan reaches out to psychiatrist Dr Jim to restore her sanity and overcome her troubled past. Yet, as Yan gradually heals, Jim finds himself haunted by the same disturbing images, as his suppressed memories resurface.

programme.title: One and Only
programme.desc: Veteran street dancer Ding Lei, invites passionate street dancer, Chen Shuo to his dance club. Sparks fly when Chen dances with the clubs top dancers. Chen pursues his dream to perform but discovers that Ding has invited him for another reason. As both of them deal with hard times, can they turn the tide on the challenges that they are facing?

programme.title: Panda Plan
programme.desc: After legendary kung fu star Jackie Chan adopts the panda Hu Hu, an international crime syndicate places a massive bounty on the bear. Joined by his agent and Hu Hus caretaker, Jackie embarks on a daring quest to outsmart the villains.

programme.title: Stand Up Story
programme.desc: Mancer knows his father Wah is intellectually challenged since young and has to take care of him after his mother left them. When Mancer discovers and finds solace in stand-up comedy, he learns that hardships provide the best comedic material - from his own school ridicule experience to pandemic woes, misery can fuel laughter!

programme.title: Coffin Homes
programme.desc: Three bizarre tales intertwine in this horror satire set against the housing crisis of Hong Kong, where soaring property prices have driven dwellers to take every insane effort necessary to secure a cramped space, even if it means sharing the same roof with the dead!

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his familys expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his familys reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: The Sparring Partner
programme.desc: Adapted from a sensational 2013 parricide in Hong Kong, a young man partners with his friend to murder and dismember his parents. Pleading not guilty, the defendants play the devil and idiot game, while the defense attorneys turn on each other. Meanwhile, heated debates emerge inside the jury room, where nine jurors grapple with the truth.

programme.title: Beauty And The 7 Beasts
programme.desc: Teddy, once a renowned movie star, is facing a career decline. To make a living, he accepts five disciples to shape them into stars. Teddys career regains momentum after he reunites with his long-lost daughter, but he is also confronted by a rival at the same time. His daughter and disciples decide to help him overcome this difficult situation

programme.title: Cyber Heist
programme.desc: Hackers have caused a large-scale cyber attack, but luckily cyber security engineer Chun, manages to fend it off with his protective firewall system. To Chun's surprise, his boss is the mastermind of the attack, and when Chun gets trapped in a money laundering operation, he must fight against his boss in the cyber world to prove his innocence.

programme.title: Only Cloud Knows
programme.desc: This romantic drama is based on the story of a real-life couple. It follows a grieving husband as he journeys to places of significance to his beloved dead wife across their New Zealand homeland.

programme.title: The Movie Emperor
programme.desc: Hong Kong megastar Lau Wai Chi aspires to win a film award. He teams up with director Lin Hao to make a film about rural China so as to win at the international film festival, and experiences local village life for the farmers role. This ends up in a series of hilarious events instead.

programme.title: All U Need is Love
programme.desc: Ten major film companies join forces on a comedy-drama film to raise funds and create jobs for industry workers during the COVID-19 pandemic. This film features an all-star ensemble cast starring for free, with the story revolving around a group of hotel guests placed under quarantine in Hong Kong.

programme.title: Moscow Mission
programme.desc: The story is based on a 1993 true event, the "China-Russia Train Robbery" where a gang of criminals commits a heist, stealing cash and goods from the cross border train. A Chinese police officer disguises as a businessman heads the operation to arrest the criminals, but uncovers a bigger conspiracy instead

programme.title: My Blue Summer
programme.desc: Zhi has been secretly in love with Nan since she met him once as a child. After graduating high school, Zhi realizes that she and Nan are in the same university, where they get to know each other by chance and become close friends. However, Zhi is still too shy to express her love for Nan. Will this long-term crush finally turn into true love?

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Shanghai
programme.desc: Ma Yong Zhen moves to Shanghai in the hope of becoming rich but ends up having to use his kung fu skills to survive and take revenge against the gang who killed his brother.

programme.title: The Infernal Walker
programme.desc: Ting is an undercover police who infiltrates a triad and Tuen is a triad mole being planted into the police force. While Tang is tired of being an undercover cop, Tuen wishes to quit the triad and become a real police. When the triad boss sets a trap to uncover the moles' identity, the two must fight for themselves.

programme.title: Inexternal
programme.desc: Ming is brutally attacked at a veterinary clinic one day and falls into a coma. In coma, he is transported to a fantasy realm where an old Master Turtle teaches him ancient boxing skills to defeat an evil boss. Meanwhile, Mings mother finds a way to save her son

programme.title: My Country, My Parents
programme.desc: Set in 4 different eras in China, the 4-part anthology about home and country is directed by Wu Jing, Zhang Zi Yi, Xu Zheng and Shen Teng, who also star in their own story. The movie depicts how the fathers forge ahead through the struggle of times, defending strong family ties and passing on the fighting spirit through generations.

programme.title: The Sword Stained With Royal Blood
programme.desc: Adapted from Jin Yong's novel, the movie depicts the havoc breaking out in the martial arts world when a warrior on the run uncovers a sword, a training manual, a treasure map and a secret message on the body of a deceased martial arts master.

programme.title: Family Light Affair
programme.desc: Alfred Cheung Kin-ting returns to the screen with this seriocomic look at the clash of cultures which result when a Mainland Chinese peasant brings his family to Hong Kong. Family Light Affair, whose Chinese title literally translates as "City Lights", is the director/writer's warm-hearted memoir of street life back in the early 1980s, featuring an eclectic cast of pop music and kung fu stars who shine in their poignant roles.

programme.title: Challenge Of The Masters
programme.desc: Young Wong Fei Hung must prove himself worthy to be taught by Master Lu, who was also his father's martial arts teacher. Although he is defeated in a competition, Wong Fei Hung's passion in Kung Fu finally moves Lu and allows him to become Lu's disciple.

programme.title: The Mad Monk
programme.desc: The movie consists of four stories of the Mad Monk helping others, from saving a mother and daughter from crumbling walls, to helping hawkers deal with bullies, recovering stolen money for a young man and punishing a devious court official and his son.

programme.title: The Savage Five
programme.desc: A group of bandits flees with a stolen safe to a village where they oppress the villagers and force the blacksmith Wei to unlock the safe. Wei refuses and flees to report to officials, while heroes of the town emerge to fight the bandits.

programme.title: The Bride From Hell
programme.desc: A young business man marries a pretty and much sought-after young bride, not knowing that she carries the spirit of a girl raped by her uncle and murdered along with her parents. Justice must be done, and it ain't pretty!

programme.title: Cat Vs Rat
programme.desc: Zhan and Bai are equally matched in martial arts skills. Bai saves the Emperor one day but did not believe in his identity and rejects a promotion. When Zhan is promoted to the royal guard after saving the Emperor, Bai gets angry and tries to prank him by stealing the imperial jade seal. Luckily, Zhan is able to retrieve the seal with his skills.

programme.title: Black Magic 2
programme.desc: Doctor Sing is puzzled by the strange symptoms of his patients and asks his friend for help. The sickness is apparently caused by a black magic that is casted by a wicked man Kong. Kong covets the beauty of Sing's wife and casts an evil love spell on her, while threatening to kill Sing at the same time. Can Sing save his wife and his patients?

programme.title: Heads For Sale
programme.desc: Hua is an upright and brave swordswoman who will stand up against villains and do anything for Luo, the man she loves. When Luo is sent to jail by the corrupted police, she sets out to free him and did not hesitate to chop off two bodyguards' heads. In the process, she also stumbles across an old enemy of her father who is back seeking revenge.

programme.title: Moonlight Serenade
programme.desc: A sweet inn-keeper's daughter is witness to a perverted rape, leading to more danger than most romantic dramas can handle. Can her true love rescue her in time? For this movie, the moonlight serenade is the sound of suspense, leading to more danger than most romantic dramas can handle.

programme.title: The Flag Of Iron
programme.desc: When super director Chang Cheh found new talent and blood with "The Five Venoms" actors, most of which were trained in the highly acrobatic Chinese opera and well versed with exotic martial arts weapons, this created a new spark for his use of bizarre weapons in his films. The Flag Of Iron is one of 20 movies that he directed featuring the utterly flabbergasting and physically exhausting action bits created by these five dudes. You have the good guys from the righteous clan versus the bad guys from the villainous clan and it's so filled with "don't-blink-or-you-will-miss-something" gags, you will need to watch it over and over again so you can see the things you missed.

programme.title: Princess Iron Fan
programme.desc: As Monkey and his gang make their way to the West through Fire Mountain, they ran into the evil Princess Iron Fan, Madam White Bone and her sexy sister, and have to fight their way through.

programme.title: Lady Of The Law
programme.desc: Chan, the chief of Wan Sheng Escort, is forced to raise his opponent's son, Yim. While Chan forbids Yim to practice martial arts, Yim secretly learns it. Ten years later, a rapist appears and Yim is arrested by a lady constable as the suspect. The rapist turns out to be Chan's elder son and Yim is framed by the Chans. Can Yim prove his innocence?

programme.title: Sons Of Good Earth
programme.desc: This is an epic tale set during the time of the Sino-Japanese war. A painter Yu saves a young girl, Lotus, who is being sold to a brothel. They fall in love, get married and settled in to a peaceful life. However, their life is soon shattered by the Japanese invasion and the brutal regime that follows...

programme.title: The Imperial Swordsman
programme.desc: Fu is a government officer heading home after being charged with falsifying reports. En route, he encounters & recruits a skilled swordsman as a bodyguard. They then meet a fleeing bride and her maid who asked to join them for protection. When the group reach a ruined temple however, a gang of assassins appear and attack them

programme.title: Hong Kong 73
programme.desc: In 1973, the Hong Kong Heng Seng Index hit extraordinary peaks and people from all walks of life go stock market crazy. Meanwhile, Hong Kong's social problems build up without anyone paying attention to what are actually happening to the crazy lives of people, in this mad city that many call home...

programme.title: Journey Of The Doomed
programme.desc: Journey Of The Doomed stars Tung Wei as a knight that finds himself protecting the life of a beautiful young lady, the lost Emperor's daughter and stalked by a bunch of assassins headed by kung fu actress extraordinaire Hui Ying-Hung.

programme.title: The Amorous Lotus Pan
programme.desc: Adapted from the renowned Chinese novel, The Water Margin, this is the story of a poor and beautiful girl Lotus Pan, who is raped by her master and had to be married off to a midget who treats her badly. Lost and lonely, Pan unwittingly becomes a pawn in the game of lust between her husband's playboy brother Wu Song, and a murderous man Men Ching.

programme.title: The Treasure Hunters
programme.desc: Fans of the international star Alexander Fu Sheng were aghast. Their idol had broken both his legs and was recuperating. Everyone wondered: would he be able to return to the action comedies for which he was so famous? This movie was the answer, and it left no doubt that he had made a full recovery. Liu Chia-yung, brother of preeminent martial arts moviemaker Liu Chia-liang, was famous in his own right for kung-fu comedies, and he out-did himself with this one. Imagine Bob Hope and Bing Crosby with the skills of Jet Li and Jackie Chan, and you've got an idea of the fun and fury inherent in this delightful tale of two con men vying for a horde of hidden gold. Add to the mix a Shaolin monk (played by "Master Killer" Gordon Liu Chia-hui), a powerfully brutal villain, and his equally dangerous mute sister (future director Yang Tsing-tsing), and you've got one of the most internationally loved kung-fu capers ever made.

programme.title: The Dream Of The Red Chamber
programme.desc: Adapted from the most widely read and filmed novel in Chinese history, this version is said to be the most successful one. Betty Loh's looks, demeanour and aura in her portrayal of Lin Dai Yu has won her the epithet "Classic Beauty".

programme.title: Come Drink With Me
programme.desc: The brother of the mystery swordswoman "Golden Swallow is kidnapped. She joins forces with a beggar Drunken Cat who is skilled in martial arts to free her brother from a Buddhist monastery run by a corrupt abbot. The film was selected as Hong Kong's entry for the Best Foreign Language Film at the 39th Academy Awards.

programme.title: The Cave Of Silken Web
programme.desc: In this third instalment of Shaw Brother's Journey to the West, Monk Tang San Zang is trapped by seven seductive spider spirits who are hell-bent on achieving immortality by eating him! Monkey, Pigsy and Sha Wu Jing have to fight the spider spirits to rescue Monk Tang San Zang.

programme.title: Young Vagabond
programme.desc: One of the great Kung-fu film characters is Beggar Su, a legendary Ching Dynasty figure who was also a member of the famous Ten Kwangtung Tigers. Little-known director Liu Shih-yu uses the best Kung-fu actors Shaw Studios had to offer to tell a rare, colorful, action-packed adventure, as Beggar Su and his brother train incessantly to defeat the brutally powerful thief called Centipede. The result is not only reminiscent of preeminent director Liu Chia-liang's work, but essentially an image to him as well.

programme.title: Rear Entrance
programme.desc: Mrs Xu is childless and watches a lonely little girl playing at the rear entrance from afar every day. She warmly nurtures the girl and even adopts her from her uncaring parent. The girl brings happiness to the Xu's until her long lost mother appears one day and to make her happy, Mrs Xu reluctantly lets the girl reunite with her mother.

programme.title: Till The End Of Time
programme.desc: This is Jenny Hu's stunning debut as a struggling singer who tries to keep her career and marriage intact. This movie also includes seven memorable hit songs.

programme.title: The Tiger And The Widow
programme.desc: The Liu Chia-liang trained Hui Ying-hung was considered the top action martial arts female star in the 1980s. It is her martial arts abilities that Michelle Yeoh tries to emulate. In The Tiger and the Widow, Hui Ying-hung is somehow mixed up in a salt smuggling ring that stinks of missing persons and rotten dilemmas.

programme.title: Tiger Killer
programme.desc: Wu Song is appointed as chief constable after killing a tiger with his bare hands when drunk. The wife of his brother Wu Da Lang, seduces Wu Song but gets rejected by him, and engages in an affair with a rich man. They poison Wu Da Lang when he finds out about their affair. To avenge his brother's death, Wu Song kills both of them.

programme.title: New Tales Of The Flying Fox
programme.desc: In a great rendition of The Silver Fox and Legend of the Fox comes this exciting adventure, where the only thing between the clan leaders and certain death is Hui Ying-hung.

programme.title: The Lark
programme.desc: Sixties pop star Carrie Ku plays the "Little Lark" in this romantic-drama of mistaken identity that is a treasure trove of some of the most popular Mandarin songs of all time.

programme.title: The Golden Knight
programme.desc: The heroine Yu Fei Xia is accused of stealing the book of martial arts secrets. To prove her innocence, she disguises herself as a man and finds her way into the Shaolin Temple to find out the truth

programme.title: Sex, Love And Hate
programme.desc: This masterpiece spins three interconnected tales about Hong Kong society's differing views on love and what women want from love. Follow a trio of Hong Kong women as they explore relationships and fulfil their hopes of finding true love.

programme.title: Five Superfighters
